Cheetor's eyes bounced back and forth between everybot that spoke, 
trying to figure out who was who and what was what and what the color 
purple tasted like. He gave a shake of his head when he heard his name 
and turned around, spotting a oh so familar bot and blinked in 
surprise. He rubbed a paw over his eyes to make sure there wasn't any 
oil in them and took a second look. 

By the Matrix, his circuits must have been fried in the battle, he was 
seeing ghostsparks. "Shadowcaster?"

OMWOS
